==== Sample Size and Power

    - *Total enrollment*: n=72 (36 ME/CFS patients + 36 matched healthy controls)
    - *ME/CFS stratification*: 12 mild, 12 moderate, 12 severe (using Bell Disability Scale)
    - *Statistical power*: $>$80% for all primary aims
    - *Attrition buffer*: 20% built into target enrollment

